-- VIP Club — Queen West Barber Co. ONE-FILE SETUP (Toronto sample)
-- Run this ENTIRE file once in the Neon SQL editor. Self-contained:
-- creates tables if missing, ADDS any columns an older schema lacked,
-- then loads the full dataset. Safe to re-run.
